{"type": "article", "id": 23386, "title": "带晕眩图案的咖啡罐包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-07T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606151551uVnEyMf7oH6pdrPq.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组咖啡包装来自澳大利亚平面设计工作室 Pop &amp; Pac，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/22490.html\">不久前我们介绍了他们设计的墨尔本高人气的咖啡馆 Operator 25 。</a>三个圆筒形的咖啡罐上都有着令人晕眩的图案，像是一圈一圈处于流动状态的波纹，非常魔幻。设计方并不想用咖啡的图案或者任何文字，仅仅以这些波纹让它们独特而有辨识度。其中红色是浓缩咖啡，蓝色是普通咖啡，绿色是速溶咖啡。<a href=\"http://www.pop-pac.com/#/project/square-one\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151549wpCYbvLKFc8G5014.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151549Uqgiw4hcCD7QvOVR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151550gvs1USfJ7VtjLueD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151550HGbOsilU20VrtQx6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}